INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2024-09-19 13:16:11','2024-09-19 13:16:11','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Trong bi cnh kinh doanh khch sn ngy cng cnh tranh gay gt, vic c mt website chuyn nghip tr thnh yu t then cht gip cc khch sn khng ch thu ht thm khch hng m cn ti u ho quy trnh qun l. Nhm p ng nhu cu , KiotViet  a ra tnh nng tng min ph tn min cho khch hng khi khi to website t phn mm qun l khch sn. y l mt gii php tin li gip nh kinh doanh tit kim chi ph, ng thi d dng s hu mt website p mt, chuyn nghip  tng cng s hin din trc tuyn v ti u ha quy trnh vn hnh.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":113023} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-kvweb.kiotviet.vn/kiotviet-website/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/19095756/phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san-18.png\" alt=\"phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san\" class=\"wp-image-113023\" title=\"phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Tn min min ph: C hi s hu website chuyn nghip</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vic h tr min ph tn min khi khch hng khi to website t phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet l mt u i hp dn. Thay v phi b ra mt khon chi ph khng nh  mua tn min, khch sn c th nhanh chng s hu mt a ch website ring, d nh v d truy cp.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":113008} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-kvweb.kiotviet.vn/kiotviet-website/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/19085511/phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san-14.png\" alt=\"phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san\" class=\"wp-image-113008\" title=\"phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt tn min d nh khng ch gip khch hng d dng tm kim m cn to dng thng hiu ring bit, gip khch sn ni bt gia hng lot i th khc. V d, thay v s dng cc nn tng min ph vi nhng tn min ph nh&nbsp;<strong>khachsanabc.wordpress.com</strong>, gi y khch sn c th s hu tn min ring nh&nbsp;<strong>khachsanabc.net</strong>. iu ny to nn s chuyn nghip v uy tn ngay t ci nhn u tin i vi khch hng tim nng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Tit kim chi ph v ti u ho quy trnh khi to website</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thng thng,  to mt website chuyn nghip cho khch sn, nh kinh doanh phi chi tr cc khon ph lin quan nh: thit k website, mua tn min, hosting, v bo tr website. Tuy nhin, khi s dng phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet, khch hng s c min ph hon ton phn tn min  mt khon chi ph ng k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>iu ny khng ch gip tit kim m cn ti u ho quy trnh khi to website. Vi s h tr t KiotViet, khch hng khng cn phi lo lng v vic ng k tn min hoc ci t phc tp, v tt c  c phn mm h tr t A n Z. Thm vo , giao din thit k website tch hp sn ca KiotViet gip ch khch sn d dng chn la mu m ph hp vi phong cch khch sn, t  nhanh chng a trang web vo hot ng m khng cn nhiu k thut chuyn mn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Xem thm:&nbsp;</strong><em><strong><a href=\"https://www.kiotviet.vn/toi-uu-hoa-trai-nghiem-khach-hang-voi-tinh-nang-tich-diem-va-quan-ly-voucher-tren-phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san-kiotviet/\">Ti u ha tri nghim khch hng vi tnh nng tch im v qun l voucher trn phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet</a></strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Tch hp y  tnh nng qun l phng trn website</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khng ch dng li  vic tng min ph tn min, website c to t phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet cn tch hp y  cc tnh nng qun l phng, cho php khch sn d dng qun l mi hot ng t mt nn tng duy nht.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trn website, khch sn c th d dng ng ti thng tin v cc loi phng, dch v, bng gi, cng vi kh nng cho php khch hng t phng trc tuyn. iu ny gip tit kim thi gian cho c khch sn ln khch hng, ng thi gim thiu sai st trong vic kim tra tnh trng phng trng.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V d, khi mt khch hng t phng qua website, h thng s t ng cp nht trng thi phng, gi thng bo xc nhn qua email v cp nht vo h thng qun l ca khch sn ngay lp tc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngoi ra, khch sn c th t do thay i thng tin trn website nh gi phng, chng trnh khuyn mi, hoc ng ti cc dch v mi m khng cn s can thip t bn th ba. y l li th rt ln gip khch sn phn ng nhanh vi nhng bin ng th trng v nhu cu khch hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Ti u ho SEO v tri nghim ngi dng</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":113009} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-kvweb.kiotviet.vn/kiotviet-website/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/19085636/phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san-15.png\" alt=\"phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san\" class=\"wp-image-113009\" title=\"phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt yu t khng th b qua khi s hu website khch sn l kh nng ti u ho cng c tm kim (SEO). Phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet tch hp cc cng c h tr SEO, gip website ca khch sn d dng ln top Google, thu ht thm nhiu lt truy cp t nhin, t  nng cao t l chuyn i, em v ngun doanh s online n nh cho khch sn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi vic cung cp tn min ring v h tr SEO, website ca khch sn s c li th ln hn khi xut hin trn cc cng c tm kim. Khch hng tim nng d dng tm thy website khch sn khi tm kim t kha lin quan, t  tng c hi t phng trc tuyn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng thi, giao din website cng c ti u ho cho cc thit b di ng. Theo thng k, phn ln khch hng hin nay tm kim v t phng qua in thoi. Vic website thn thin vi thit b di ng khng ch ci thin tri nghim ngi dng m cn to iu kin thun li  khch hng thc hin t phng nhanh chng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Xem thm:&nbsp;</strong><em><strong><a href=\"https://www.kiotviet.vn/phan-mem-quan-ly-khach-san-kiotviet-tu-dong-hoa-quy-trinh-dat-phong-truc-tuyen/\">Phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet: T ng ha quy trnh t phng trc tuyn</a></strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet: Sn sng cho qu trnh pht trin lu di</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>S hu website chuyn nghip v tn min ring khng ch mang li li ch trc mt m cn l mt bc u t cho s pht trin lu di ca khch sn. Vi vic to dng thng hiu trc tuyn mnh m, khch sn d dng thu ht thm nhiu i tng khch hng tim nng, m rng th trng v tng cng kh nng cnh tranh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khng ch vy, vic s dng phn mm qun l khch sn KiotViet cn gip h thng ho v t ng ho quy trnh qun l, t  gip khch sn ti u ho chi ph v nng cao cht lng dch v.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dng th min ph</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Vic KiotViet h tr tng min ph tn min khi khch hng khi to website t&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.kiotviet.vn/nha-nghi-khach-san-homestay-villa/\">phn mm qun l khch sn</a></strong>&nbsp;l mt tnh nng u vit, mang li nhiu li ch thit thc cho qu trnh kinh doanh. T vic tit kim chi ph, d dng khi to website, n vic tch hp cc tnh nng qun l phng, KiotViet mang n gii php ton din gip khch sn khng ch pht trin bn vng m cn vn xa hn trn th trng trc tuyn y tim nng.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','KiotViet tng MIN PH tn min cho khch hng khi to website t phn mm qun l khch sn','','publish','open','open','','chao-moi-nguoi','','','2024-09-19 14:12:04','2024-09-19 14:12:04','',0,'http://localhost:5000/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(3,1,'2024-09-19 13:16:11','2024-09-19 13:16:11','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. Mc ch v phm vi thu thp</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>iOrder yu cu khch hng cung cp cc thng tin c bn bao gm: email, in thoi, tn ng nhp, mt khu ng nhp, a ch khi khch hng ng k s dng dch v ca iOrder v mt s thng tin khng bt buc khc khi khch hng mun tng tc vi mt s ni dung trn website v ng dng iOrder. iOrder s dng cc thng tin ny nhm lin h xc nhn vi khch hng v m bo quyn li cho Khch hng khi cn thit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vic bn truy cp, ng k, s dng iOrder c ngha rng bn ng  v chp nhn rng buc bi cc quy nh trong chnh sch bo mt ca chng ti.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khch hng s t chu trch nhim v bo mt v lu gi mi hot ng s dng dch v di tn ng k, mt khu v hp th in t v/hoc s in thoi ca mnh. iOrder khng chu trch nhim v cc tht thot d liu, b mt thng tin ca khch hng do khch hng v tnh hoc c  gy ra. Ngoi ra, Khch hng c trch nhim thng bo kp thi cho iOrder v nhng hnh vi s dng tri php, lm dng, vi phm bo mt, lu gi tn ng k v mt khu ca bn th ba  c bin php gii quyt ph hp.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. Dch v, ng dng lin kt vi iOrder</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> m bo quyn li v tri nghim tt nht cho Khch hng, iOrder p dng mt s iu khon ring khi Khch hng s dng cc dch v, ng dng do iOrder cung cp hoc c lin kt vi iOrder:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>A. <u>i vi khch hng s dng ng dng iOrder t Apple App Store hoc GooglePlay, bn hiu v chp nhn rng iOrder c quyn:</u></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) Ly v tri hin ti ca bn;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2) Ghi d liu ca ng dng iOrder ln th nh;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3) Truy cp vo Internet t thit b ca bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tt c cc truy cp ny ch c chng ti thc hin khi c s ng  ca bn. Bn hiu va chp nhn rng, khi bn  cp quyn cho chng ti, bn s khng c bt k khiu ni no i vi vic truy cp ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>B. <u>i vi ti khon Facebook ca Khch hng khi lin kt iOrder, iOrder s yu cu quyn truy cp cc thng tin sau:</u></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) Quyn truy cp vo a ch email ca Trang (Fan Page) Facebook s dng  tch hp vi iOrder;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2) Quyn truy cp vo tp hp cc mc cng khai trn Trang Facebook  tch hp vi iOrder;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3) Cho php truy cp vo tp hp cc mc cng khai trn Ti khon c nhn ca ngi dng c tng tc vi Trang Facebook tch hp vi iOrder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4) Cho php truy cp hp th trn Trang Facebook tch hp vi iOrder thng qua iOrder;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5) Cho php gi v nhn tin nhn, bnh lun trn Trang Facebook tch hp vi iOrder thng qua iOrder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>C. <u>i vi ti khon Zalo ca Khch hng khi lin kt vi iOrder, iOrder s yu cu quyn truy cp cc thng tin sau:</u></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) Quyn truy cp vo nh i din, tn, nh ba v m t ca ti khon Zalo Official Account s dng  tch hp vi iOrder;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2) Quyn truy cp vo thng tin h tn, a ch, s in thoi ca ngi dng theo di (follow) ti khon Zalo Official account s dng tch hp vi iOrder;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3) Cho php gi v nhn tin nhn t ti khon Zalo Official Account tch hp vi iOrder thng qua iOrder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. Phm vi s dng thng tin</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>iOrder s dng thng tin Khch hng cung cp :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Cung cp cc dch v n Khch hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Gi cc thng bo v cc hot ng trao i thng tin gia Khch hng v n v H tr k thut ca iOrder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Ngn nga cc hot ng ph hy ti khon ngi dng ca Khch hng hoc cc hot ng gi mo Khch hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Lin lc v gii quyt vi khch hng trong nhng trng hp c bit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> iOrder c trch nhim hp tc cung cp thng tin c nhn Khch hng khi c yu cu t c quan nh nc c thm quyn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Chia s thng tin cn thit cho bn i tc nu nhn c s ng  ca Khch hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. Thi gian lu tr thng tin</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong mi trng hp thng tin c nhn Khch hng s c bo mt hon ton trn my ch ca iOrder. Khch hng c quyn cp nht, sa i v xa thng tin ca cc D liu c nhn ny. Tuy nhin, trong mt s trng hp, iOrder vn c th khi phc nhng thng tin  t c s d liu ca chng ti  gii quyt cc tranh chp, thi hnh iu khon s dng, hay v cc yu cu k thut, php l lin quan n s an ton v nhng hot ng ca iOrder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. a ch ca n v thu thp, qun l thng tin v h tr Khch hng</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>CNG TY C PHN CNG NGH iOrder</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>a ch: 756A u C - Phng 14 - Q Tn Bnh - HCM</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hotline: 02871073999</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Email: contact@iorder.vn</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>6. Phng tin v cng c  Khch hng tip cn v chnh sa d liu ca mnh</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khch hng c quyn t kim tra, cp nht, iu chnh thng tin c nhn ca mnh bng cch ng nhp vo ti khon v chnh sa thng tin c nhn hoc yu cu iOrder thc hin vic ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khch hng c quyn gi khiu ni 